data.description: How about a new place to call home for your new year? Come check out this wonderful multi-level in Bennington Schools. Notice the cute front landing that leads into the house. The front room boasts tall cathedral ceilings with an open floor plan. The kitchen has SS appliances which all stay, gas cooktop, ample cabinets & pantry. Notice the large eating area. The primary bedroom has a private ¾ bathroom. Nice closet space and ceiling fan. The lower level has a cozy fireplace & a great place to make an office or an additional FR. The lowest level is perfect with ample storage room and houses the W & D. Home already has a radon system. Furnace features a new circuit board. Notice all of the windows have custom blinds. There is a new spring on the garage door. The private backyard is fully fenced with sprinkler system. Trampoline and shelving in the garage and LL are negotiable. Roof replaced 2017 with upgraded shingles. Come see this great find!
